喜歡她的黑色的BRA，維多利亞的秘密的，可惜壓壞了。她的耳朵是敏感點，RT也挺敏感的。她水很多很舒服， 還有，第一次的時候我們在學校門口200塊的小旅館做的，她疼的撕心裂肺氣若遊絲，手把我的背都抓破了。第一次的時候超級緊，我好不容易才插進去，看到她流血我好心疼。不過你放心，我已經幫你拓寬了，你進入輕鬆多了，也不用看著她受罪心疼了。不用感謝我，畢竟她幸福就好。好像也沒什麼了，就這些吧祝你們幸福哈。對了，你們牽手的時候別想她的手摸過我的老二， 對了，你們親嘴的時候別想她的嘴巴被我的老二塞滿過，開心點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"ece3d2c3cd18b0d062bd5c46dcffcbf7734d908e","tid":441844,"uid":44329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T07:12:53.000Z","msg":"佢前度有冇屌過你應該一入就知"},{"pid":"59efd637a87fa679ed4c203c763dd56a6451277c","tid":441844,"uid":73443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T07:13:46.000Z","msg":"叫佢中出返係咪第一次囉"},{"pid":"e7deb08e92aeb87615bf82c105cf33349985de15","tid":441844,"uid":137847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T07:16:13.000Z","msg":"佢係咪唔夠愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e5f6e6a3ba9071ab715b25a225a405c78c2ac1","tid":441844,"uid":21514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T07:16:38.000Z","msg":"O2 not A1"},{"pid":"7ca6824482990c61a51a151f3322e55949386fb3","tid":441844,"uid":34468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T07:19:19.000Z","msg":"分左手"},{"pid":"c2fab58d946e8576fd6f9b3039c762acad6434e1","tid":441844,"uid":55519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T07:19:24.000Z","msg":"佢應該中意前度多過你"},{"pid":"b6099c87e794c9f9aaf1c70de6491254c82b4a8e","tid":441844,"uid":34468,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T07:19:48.000Z","msg":"分左手就A2, 未就A2<br />\n點A1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5178ec0ec058a49778b749e9744a811e838bdfc","tid":441844,"uid":34468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T07:20:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分左手就A2, 未就O2<br />\n點A1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif